    "name": "Cloudy with a Chance of Kittens",
    "steam_appid": 3237870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/ba1b103535353bab22e77f3a0de36340.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=530 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/ba1b103535353bab22e77f3a0de36340.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/ba1b103535353bab22e77f3a0de36340.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merge adorable dessert-shaped cats to create larger felines, all the way up to the ultimate cat-ermelon! Collect points to unlock exciting power-ups and customize your gameplay. Play casually for fun or take on challenges as you navigate obstacles and changing weather conditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/7163470cae08710098b434e881f60a48.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/7163470cae08710098b434e881f60a48.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/7163470cae08710098b434e881f60a48.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/49e820bdf89fd2f1eb9b41a300c1c6ab.webp?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/e9eccad063f208ca81142ad109498f0b.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0d1d1a6a53af5814348db92205e41bb7.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0d1d1a6a53af5814348db92205e41bb7.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0d1d1a6a53af5814348db92205e41bb7.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exciting Power-ups:</strong> Rack up points to unlock a variety of fun power-ups! Shrink large cats, clear away cats blocking your merges, influence the weather conditions, and use other handy boosts to maximize your score and combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/ba0c6b06a201f6bb62ff3cddd5d1b226.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=100 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/914f3931ee8d8128c5133cefd41128ce.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/914f3931ee8d8128c5133cefd41128ce.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/914f3931ee8d8128c5133cefd41128ce.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxed Play or Optional Challenges:</strong> Whether you’re here to relax or seek a challenge, we’ve got you covered! Play at your own pace without time limits or obstacles, or, if you’re up for it, dive into exciting challenges. Face a countdown timer, overcome falling objects, and navigate changing weather conditions that bring fresh twists to the game’s physics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/117725ad24502c374da745e0f7346fc0.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=100 /></span><strong>Fun Leaderboards:</strong> Set new high scores and secure your spot on the leaderboard! Each game mode offers its unique leaderboard - challenge yourself to rise to the top in every style of play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/65d8e5bedd524d12388c919b4b6c02eb.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=170 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/65d8e5bedd524d12388c919b4b6c02eb.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/65d8e5bedd524d12388c919b4b6c02eb.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0840d704d03d3bde3239d074d518cd54.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/5cfe10965e6d476587e5536432d98838.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/5cfe10965e6d476587e5536432d98838.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/5cfe10965e6d476587e5536432d98838.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enhanced Physics:</strong> Experience dynamic physics that makes the gameplay truly engaging! Experiment with spinning, bouncing, weight variations, and more. Drop cats at different angles or with acceleration to discover unique effects and try creative merging strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/c9829fbcf4e2789e05d0a78d2bd8154c.webp?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0980ed1f28debd1cdc556fe571ba3173.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0311138f39bd97b61225bb64a6ed3cb6.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0311138f39bd97b61225bb64a6ed3cb6.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0311138f39bd97b61225bb64a6ed3cb6.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxed Mode:</strong> Unwind and play at your own pace! Explore the game’s physics, experiment with combos and power-ups, and enjoy the gameplay free from time limits or obstacles. Perfect for a cozy, stress-free experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/58f9a885ce6ae61359e024235aa6df80.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0f4182545f5c8c8927606cbda8b50868.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0f4182545f5c8c8927606cbda8b50868.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/0f4182545f5c8c8927606cbda8b50868.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Mode:</strong> Race against the clock to score as many points as possible before the timer runs out! Overcome playful obstacles falling from the sky. Make clever merges and chain combos to earn bonus time and keep the fun going. How long can you last?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/f7d16f0856562e1b2a072ededa295269.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/82b6686eb0b3262c0463a6a469e6ab97.poster.avif?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/82b6686eb0b3262c0463a6a469e6ab97.webm?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/82b6686eb0b3262c0463a6a469e6ab97.mp4?t=1772111772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weather Mode:</strong> Experiment with the game’s physics in varying weather conditions! Navigate through changing winds, clouds, and downpours as you make merges and combos. Use your power-ups strategically to adapt and thrive in this unpredictable environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237870/extras/1bc4aa592fe9646f7a075088b328f14b.webp?t=1772111772\" width=620 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can I play this game if I’m allergic to cats?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course! Our cats were carefully bred to be 100% hypoallergenic and 50% dessert. Just don’t lick the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why do cats fall from the clouds?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity. They tried floating once but complained it wasn’t dignified enough.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Is this game scientifically accurate?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absolutely. It’s peer-reviewed by at least three cats who occasionally sit on our keyboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can I pet the cats in the game?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, but you’ll need a touchscreen or a very precise mouse. Don’t pet too hard, or you’ll smear the frosting.</p>",
